description: ORDER granting Defendants'  64  motion to dismiss.  For the reasons stated in the attached Memorandum and Order, the Court grants Defendants' motion to dismiss for insufficient service with respect to Defendant Rachel Stiene and dismisses P laintiffs' claims against her without prejudice.  The Court further grants Defendants' motion to dismiss for failure to state a claim with respect to Defendant Erik Stiene and dismisses Plaintiffs' claims against him with prejudice.  Plaintiffs are denied leave to amend.The Clerk of Court is respectfully requested to enter judgment in favor of Defendants and close this case.  Ordered by Judge Kiyo A. Matsumoto on 4/17/2024.
